data.description: Just in time for the US Open, here is your chance to own a low-maintenance home minutes from Pinehurst Resort! This beautifully renovated townhome is located in the desirable Lawn and Tennis Club Community. This is a must see 4-bedroom complete with wood burning fireplace, designated laundry room, two car garage, and maintenance-free backyard oasis. HOA dues provide Spectrum internet and cable.  The main living/dining area features an open floor plan, one-of-a-kind reclaimed wood, and a built-in bar complete with wine fridge! All bedrooms reside on the second floor. Separate heating and cooling for each floor. HVAC for upstairs 2021, and brand new 2024 for downstairs. Garage features built-in shelving and epoxy floor coating. Brand new plumbing was just installed throughout crawlspace. Appliances included! Conveniently located to shops, restaurants and in the heart of golf mecca. Schedule a showing today before it's gone!
